title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your emotions are likely all over the place today. It might be hard to settle into your work as you're sad one moment and elated the next. However, youre possibly contending with deep doubts about your own abilities and qualifications. Perhaps you sense that youre not living up to your full potential, and you may feel your ability to do something about it is slipping from your grasp. Yet, the most authentic moment for any lasting change in your life is right now. Focus on your current blessings to create the future of your dreams. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
